Okay so I read that the audio wasn't the best on this, so I decided to try it with headphones. What a mistake. All I hear is the sound of the person recording the video clearing their throat, sniffling, and the occasional nasal whistle. Then there's the constant repetitious sound of fabric rustling in the background, which is a bit disconcerting. Either he's tapping his fot the whole time while wearing Adidas pants or he's rubbing one out lol.

Side note though, video quality is very good for a cam and audio is understandable, but don't use headphones, lol.
